data.description: Welcome to this beautiful home on a culdesac in a wonderful neighborhood in Monroeville. The property has been updated and has plenty to offer including peace of mind with a new roof and a completely updated electrical box and service. The property has had many updates as they have rejuvenated the beautiful wood floors in this home that you can see from the charming light that comes through all the windows. The home is a simple ranch design with a large living room and a kitchen and dining room that make for easy sightlines. The kitchen updates include brand-new cabinets and new flooring. The bathroom has been updated as well. The bedrooms are great size with updated windows and great closet space. There is a large basement the footprint of the home with a second bathroom as well. Convenient to shopping and PA turnpike, Parkway East, restaurants, medical facilities and parks.
